data.description:
Welcome to this beautifully updated 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom condo that offers more than just a place to live; This lovely condo boasts a host of features that are sure to make you fall in love.

Step inside to find a space that has been thoughtfully updated with new flooring, giving it a fresh and modern feel. The vaulted ceiling adds a touch of elegance and opens up the room, making it feel incredibly inviting. The kitchen peninsula is perfect for hosting friends and family, creating memories over delicious meals. With the Mini-split A/C with a heat pump you'll stay cool in the summer and warm in the winter, all while saving on energy costs.

The HOA fee is $175, covering essential services like lawn care, snow removal, and building insurance.
